rawContent:
We started our depression unit.
Me: "Sometimes feeling depressed doesn't look like big feelings.  Sometimes it looks like not showering or brushing your teeth for a week."
Student mumbles: "That is real.  That is real."

Depression swallows people up!  

#depression #teach
